Its purpose is to develop Non-Kinetic Cyber Effects (NKCE) support to Long Range Kill Chains. This is accomplished by increasing fielded technologies focused on
increased aircraft survivability and munitions effectiveness to achieve tactical air objectives. The initiative transitions these efforts from laboratories, industry, and
academia through studies, accelerated prototyping, and technology demonstrations. To accomplish its mission, success relies on balanced efforts across three Air Force
