FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
A budget increase of $40.975M (from $30.893M to $71.868M) supports increased efforts under the DCWO
portfolio resulting from successful Science & Technology developments and support of an USAF Urgent
Operational Need. These successful S&T activities address critical warfighting gaps, are ready for maturation
into operationally relevant, executable systems and are supportive of Long Range Kill Chains for active-duty
units.
