Description: The NIXIE HK System is an all-encompassing threat torpedo Countermeasure system that
provides a torpedo hard kill capability to the Surface Navy. The System includes all the capabilities of the AN/
SLQ-25 NIXIE 25E System, the fire control Capability, and includes the capability to launch a CRAW as the
weapon to produce the HK capability. NIXIE HK system launcher will also include the ability to launch ADC MK2
(series) devices.

