D. Acquisition Strategy
- CV-TSC utilizes an incremental development approach that aims to deliver capability updates via Fleet Capability Releases (FCRs). This approach allows required
capability to be delivered to address emerging Fleet needs and provides frequent opportunities to ensure interoperability is synchronized with the SSDS and other critical
ship-board systems. The acquisition strategy places heavy emphasis on the use of standardized combat system hardware and software hosting, minimizing the use of
custom hardware thereby reducing life-cycle costs.




