decision-grade analysis of enterprise IT shortfalls and emerging enterprise solutions impacting the Combatant Commands' joint
warfighting mission. The reduction will impact EMSO's capacity to employ its cloud-based Assessment Environment and Digital
Architecture Library, decreasing the accuracy and timeliness of its data analysis and digital assessments and failing to advance
OUSW(I&S) Digital Transformation of the Defense Intelligence Enterprise.
FY 2027 Plans:
Cancellation of efforts: The termination of funding across the FYDP, combined with the loss of the CCI EMSO RDT&E budget,
will prevent the team from delivering decision-grade analysis of enterprise IT shortfalls and emerging enterprise solutions critical
to the Combatant Commands' joint warfighting mission. EMSO will no longer be able to support its cloud-based Assessment
Environment and Digital Architecture Library, severely compromising the accuracy and timeliness of data analysis and digital

