D. Acquisition Strategy
Air Force Life Cycle Management Center/Intelligence, Surveillance, and Reconnaissance and Special Operations Forces Directorate (AFLCMC/WI) will execute
COMPASS BRIGHT efforts through technology maturation contracts. COMPASS BRIGHT leverages existing relationships with mission partners to mature SIGINT and
MASINT technology for ASE.

 On an annual basis, the SIGINT Capabilities Working Group (SCWG) reviews developmental technologies against warfighter capabilities and requirements based on
 strategic roadmaps. SIGINT and MASINT proposals are evaluated and prioritized into a recommended list for senior executive direction to implement for the coming
 fiscal year.



