Description: MTRS is a multifunction ATC surveillance sensor to support expeditionary operations. Supports Air Traffic Control
Surveillance, Battle Management Command and Control (BMC2), Unmanned Aircraft Systems (UAS) surveillance/domain
awareness, and weather sensing missions. This new multifunction ATC radar will have a lower total footprint and lifecycle costs.
The MTRS program captures AFT technology demonstration results and continues system development as a stand-alone
technology project.

FY 2026 Plans:
