- Continue Lightweight Deployable-Instrument Landing System (LD-ILS) localizer array proof-of-concept testing
for Small Footprint - Precision Approach Landing Capability (SF-PALC) efforts
- Begin mechanical packaging of the complete LD-ILS into a more compact, deployable end-item
- Start test and evaluation of flight inspection drones
- Complete operational assessment of Mobile Air Traffic System (MATS) software
