Title: MW/MT Enhancement                                                                                                                 13.235      12.783         13.322
Description: Integrate new data source to include Ballistic Missile Defense Communication Node (BCN) and Ground-Based
Midcourse Defense (GMD) Communications Network (GCN) of the Missile Defense Agency (MDA) C2BMC integration element
of the Ballistic Missile Defense System (BMDS). Enhance existing displays by incorporating new sensor with existing data,
modernize database content with additional multi-domain meta-data to improve threat assessment, attack characterizations
to address new sensor data. Improves source data accuracy for missile warning mission and translate for integration into the
Combatant Commanders Integrated Command and Control System (CCIC2S) that will enhance mission displays and improve
impact prediction. Creates multiple display options for the operator and reduces ambiguity between missile defense and missile
warning displays.

FY 2026 Plans:
Complete integration of first non-traditional data source to provide event-tracking and common operating picture.

Conduct formal developmental test and evaluation.

Start integration of one new (space message) data source from the Ballistic Missile Defense Communication Node (BCN) and
Ground-Based Midcourse Defense (GMD) Communications Network (GCN) of the Missile Defense Agency (MDA) Command and
Control, Battle Management, and Communications (C2BMC) integration element of the Ballistic Missile Defense System (BMDS).

Rapidly respond to implement system resiliency and situational awareness necessary to operate in the contested space domain.
Activities may include, but are not limited to program office support, studies, technical analysis, experimentation, risk reduction,
prototyping, and activities that may leverage commercial, U.S. Government partnership, and international opportunities to respond
to existing and emerging adversarial threats with speed and agility.
FY 2027 Plans:
Complete integration of one new (space message) data source from the Ballistic Missile Defense Communication Node (BCN)
and Ground-Based Midcourse Defense (GMD) Communications Network (GCN) of the Missile Defense Agency (MDA) Command
and Control, Battle Management, and Communications (C2BMC) integration element of the Ballistic Missile Defense System
(BMDS).

Conduct formal developmental test and evaluation on first space message data source.

Operational Systems Development

